title: (Tánaiste and Minister for Enterprise, Trade and Employment) (No. 2) Order
(Tánaiste and Minister for Enterprise, Trade and Employment) (No. 2) Order
heading: 2. Cliona Doyle, particulars of whose address have been deposited at the
text_raw:
2. Cliona Doyle, particulars of whose address have been deposited at the 
offices of the Department of Enterprise, Trade and Employment, is appointed 
to be a Special Adviser to the Tánaiste and Minister for Enterprise, Trade and 
Employment with effect from 1 November 2022. 

GIVEN under the Official Seal of the Government, 

25 October, 2022. 

MICHEÁL MARTIN, 

Taoiseach. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 28th October, 2022.
